page.title: 23A Colehill Girls Day
page.content:
Early in the morning I get up at 7.00am. I go downstairs to get my breakfast then I go back up to get dressed. I gather all my bags together and I go to school.

Today is Monday and in the morning I am part of the hall team and I set it up ready for Well Done Assembly. In the afternoon I do Multi Sports - it is fun!

At the end of the day I gather my bags and go home. I have a nice teacher and teaching assistant.

I had lots of fun today.
